{"data":[{"id":557774031,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fbc1661039fe84e3d0eae8ee359d98e5","url_token":"reciprocity","name":"Reciprocity","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fbc1661039fe84e3d0eae8ee359d98e5","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557774031","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545527876,"updated_time":1545527876,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":23,"content":"\u003cp\u003e1. 如果你只用初等数论知识完成的证明，建议放弃。因为证明错的概率是99.999999%，话说回来，即使你的证明没有问题，一个很严肃的问题是你很难找到一个大学数学老师来花时间验证这个东西。民科或许愿意，但民科一样无法获得主流学术界的认同。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2. 如果你的英文还可以，建议将其翻译成英文，挂在arxiv上。挂上去之后你对这个享有完全的著作权，不必担心抄袭问题，同时向国际顶级期刊投稿，如Ann. Math, JAMS, Acta Math等等。怀尔斯的费马大定理的证明就是在Ann. Math. 上发表的哦。一旦在这种期刊上发表，就宣告了你的证明的正确性。而不是像其他答主贴图一样，发表在国内水杂志上，并没有任何卵用\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561125622,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"02acef6decdaa13dfd3a903c87a52850","url_token":"yang-wei-can-22","name":"栗山","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b7ea8c1bb2dd684611ea1d75ef9c22fd_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b7ea8c1bb2dd684611ea1d75ef9c22fd_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/02acef6decdaa13dfd3a903c87a52850","user_type":"people","headline":"物理专业学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561125622","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545919089,"updated_time":1545919089,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":17,"content":"\u003cp\u003e2019年快到了，你最担心的是______\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e❌没钱过年\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e❌中美合拍电影上映了没\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e⭕题主的论文发表了没\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e❌世界末日\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561305595,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7240b2ae38836f4837c2d7355b2ee72d","url_token":"pansz","name":"pansz","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/310d85e8d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/310d85e8d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7240b2ae38836f4837c2d7355b2ee72d","user_type":"people","headline":"我说的大多是一本道","badge":[{"type":"best_answerer","description":"优秀回答者","topics":[]}],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561305595","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545956949,"updated_time":1545957390,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":241,"content":"\u003cp\u003e可以认真的肯定的说，\u003cb\u003e不会\u003c/b\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先我们假设他\u003cb\u003e真的证明\u003c/b\u003e了，然后他需要发表论文以公布自己的证明，这篇论文需要经过同行审核，发表，可能需要几年，发表之后再经过同行评议，讨论验证，然后在学术交流会上讨论，5~7年，甚至更长的时间后，才会被学术界完全认可，届时他都已经大学毕业了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e历史上多个年轻数学家作出的重大证明，都是经过了很多年以后才被学术界认可的。比方说五次方程没有通用解析解公式这个，某个年轻数学家证明了它，却花了一辈子没有等来学术界的承认。直到后来。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e给大家一个时间参考：陈景润在1965年证明了数论（1+2），1966年发表，1973年才获得学术界轰动，1978年才得奖。\u003cb\u003e从证明到得奖耗费了13年\u003c/b\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，\u003cb\u003e一个高中生就算证明了哥德巴赫猜想，对保送清北也没有任何价值\u003c/b\u003e，这个证明要等到学术界广泛承认，他早就已经大学毕业了，在被学术界广泛承认之前，他的证明只能被当做痴人说梦而忽略，不可能被用于保送。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562561762,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562561762","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-5ec9a45a77b51ef798d38a1b584ed2e0_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546100707,"updated_time":1546100707,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e那啥，我这也有一些发明，你看能不能帮忙一块发表一下，我也想上清华：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-66caa8c793046c9d38a49e9a1af7641e_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"440\" data-rawheight=\"2947\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-66caa8c793046c9d38a49e9a1af7641e_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"440\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-66caa8c793046c9d38a49e9a1af7641e_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='440'%20height='2947'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"440\" data-rawheight=\"2947\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-66caa8c793046c9d38a49e9a1af7641e_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"440\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-66caa8c793046c9d38a49e9a1af7641e_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-66caa8c793046c9d38a49e9a1af7641e_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563277182,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"88fd9dd045a1f0cc444c6df3963c8bdf","url_token":"liu-ming-yu-37-63","name":"杜祭酒","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ba47e6a8da9beb71f4688a69b4d40ad6_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ba47e6a8da9beb71f4688a69b4d40ad6_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/88fd9dd045a1f0cc444c6df3963c8bdf","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563277182","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546220350,"updated_time":1546260446,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":49,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这样\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主2019年1月1日如期发表论文并\u003cb\u003e正确证出哥德巴赫猜想了\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我将从  \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e关注我/在此帖下回复我  \u003c/b\u003e   的人们中\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e随机抽奖抽出一人 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e送iPhone Xs Max/华为 mate20 pro\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（那个人可自己选）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再随机抽10人发666元现金红包\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（毕竟，要是题主正确证明了，我等有幸见证伟人和奇迹诞生，太值得庆贺啦，我一个穷人破破费给大家乐上加乐，荣幸至极。）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主\u003cb\u003e没有\u003c/b\u003e正确证出哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们取关他取关问题并举报他\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e怎么样\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-651cdce9308b925fcf4c4c7825e4d631_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"48\" data-rawheight=\"48\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"48\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='48'%20height='48'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"48\" data-rawheight=\"48\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"48\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-651cdce9308b925fcf4c4c7825e4d631_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e我很真诚的！（严肃脸）\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个答案是我抖机灵写下的，恕本人才疏学浅，连照猫画虎都画不好，何等笨拙的“吸粉”啊……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e事情结束了大家都把我取关了吧……否则小生不胜惶恐 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560661653,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560661653","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545877651,"updated_time":1545877651,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":13,"content":"\u003cp\u003e没有想到这个问题引起了不少关注，甚至不少回答者做出了各色各样的回答，当然无论嘲讽，讥笑，批判，鼓励，原本以为只是个脑洞题，没想到确实是有人真实的内心问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我无法就这个问题给出回答，但是可以反过来给予一定的思考:进入清华北大，数学方面就能做出巨大的成就吗，答案自然是否定的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e今年刚好是中科院20周年庆，科院回顾了相关领域的成果，摘取部分如下:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e席南华对仿射A型Weyl群证明了Lusztig关于基环的猜想，成为国际上很多后续工作的基础之一\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e周向宇带领研究生解决了多复变中的“经典问题”最优L2延拓问题、证明了Demailly强开性猜想，在美国《数学评论》上被评论为“近年来多复变与代数几何领域最伟大的成就之一”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“新生代”数学家田野首次给出7个千禧数学问题之一“椭圆曲线BSD猜想”的重要线索\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e人称“论证骑士”的孙斌勇与李文威对朗兰兹纲领一系列重要问题的探索，以及青年学者黄飞敏在玻尔兹曼方程的流体力学方面，都取得了重要的突破\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e冯康独立于西方创始了有限元方法，在国际上首次提出基于辛几何原理计算哈密尔顿体系的新方法\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e袁亚湘等最早使用子空间技术分析计算方法，相继提出了子空间共轭梯度法、非线性优化子空间法与子空间拟牛顿法等方法。该方法被称为Dai-Yuan方法，并且与FR方法、HS方法、PRP方法并列，被认为是“四个主要方法”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e张平和黄飞敏团队证明了各向异性不可压缩Navier-Stokes方程整体适定性；证明了在黎曼解这一重要情形下Boltzmann方程的极限是可压缩Euler方程\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e插一个故事（我听彭实戈讲过一个故事:他高中的时候正好哥猜流行，他的许多同学那时候也兴致勃勃，想要在这方面一展身手，但大多数后来就放弃了，后来他知识青年下乡，经常捧着一本苏联某数学课本看，周围没有几个懂数学的，不会的问题经常是跑几个村子去找能够解答的人讨论）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e观看他们的履历不难发现，绝大多数不是清北出身，当然北大出身自然也有做出了很多巨大成就的，但是无一例外不是在各自领域深耕数十年，现代数学的庞杂性远超过很多人的理解，提及数学绝不是只有哥猜甚至是囿于基础数学领域，大概率的结果是对于非基础数学领域的其他数学工作者，相关领域的突破要比哥猜来的重要些。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果真要证明自己的价值，不是非要攀登数学的几座顶峰，那上面容易缺氧窒息而亡，不如先爬几座山头，锻炼一下身体，在决定是否要那些方向走。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559450525,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b4df3211787dfb5619ba77b4334e7e9f","url_token":"long-shen-tian-wu","name":"龙神天舞","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b4df3211787dfb5619ba77b4334e7e9f","user_type":"people","headline":"想飞上天空","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559450525","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545727960,"updated_time":1545727960,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":254,"content":"\u003cp\u003e啥意思啊？只用淘宝货就造出了一颗热核聚变弹头后问能不能保送清华核物理工程专业吗？我觉得可以和清华的学生同一个教室上课，他们坐着，你前面站着。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563423050,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563423050","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546235427,"updated_time":1546235740,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":29,"content":"\u003cp\u003e微分不是积分，极值不是最值。 泰勒展开比洛必达公式好用，我用泰勒从28项展开到82项，我太了解他了！ 我刚刚进来的时候，有个学生就问我，sin|x|函数的图像怎么画啊？我们说一个数学考试没有自己的公式是可悲的，有了公式还不去用就是可耻的。年轻的考生还在笑，我是笑不出来。有的考生一看到题，第一反应“哇，太难了！”这怎么行呢？见到难题，尤其需要乐观向上。经常有小朋友过来问我，洛必达法则到底有几个条件啊？我看有些教材，洛必达竟然和拉格朗日谈起了恋爱，洛必达叫拉格朗日叫日日，拉格朗日叫洛必达叫达达，求导不分，积分颠倒。这样的教材主创人员是要向全国人民谢罪的！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有些考生竟然还带了两张准考证，结果一进考场就被拦下来了。你说你要证哥德巴赫猜想，有本事上台来我们俩比划比划。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是身经百战见得多了，我研究了十七年的高数，每年稿费不到70元，十七年下来不到2000元。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561182548,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"6223d66a7b7644b42ba3ddb523453e39","url_token":"lqcgreat","name":"小林桑","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7d593a40fe3af8e92665f279f844c8fa_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7d593a40fe3af8e92665f279f844c8fa_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/6223d66a7b7644b42ba3ddb523453e39","user_type":"people","headline":"爱好广泛的可爱正太","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561182548","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-70c724d2398d35af24e83abe8b81da63_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545924315,"updated_time":1546326831,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":41,"content":"\u003cp\u003e到一月一号波函数就坍塌了 到时候大家看结果吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1.1更新\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他把证明删了 果断搬运 不谢\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e———————————————分割线——\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第一部分：思路:有借有还，再借不难。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e分类讨论，逐一判断。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e准备:1.设集合A为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数包括正质数和负质数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2.设集合B为所有满足两个质数之和的偶数的集合。且此时质数只包括正质数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3.任意大于等于4的偶数均可以表示为(6k-2),6k,(6k+2)中的一种。其中k为正整数。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e目的:证明任意n∈正整数且n＞＝2时，2n∈B是真命题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第二部分：证明\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7db478772e42c15d827c61ef50ab4b82_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c46ac0a3da84406602101a148e0470fd_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7db478772e42c15d827c61ef50ab4b82_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c46ac0a3da84406602101a148e0470fd_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7db478772e42c15d827c61ef50ab4b82_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-7db478772e42c15d827c61ef50ab4b82_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-73422ee11211cf9e68952422d6778ef7_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4b52cce3fb5e1ef51b9d1512085f4679_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-73422ee11211cf9e68952422d6778ef7_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4b52cce3fb5e1ef51b9d1512085f4679_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-73422ee11211cf9e68952422d6778ef7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-73422ee11211cf9e68952422d6778ef7_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-68c46eb1afb556cc00704af32674e84a_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-946c18b34f06739be7d22e639f5a7052_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-68c46eb1afb556cc00704af32674e84a_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-946c18b34f06739be7d22e639f5a7052_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-68c46eb1afb556cc00704af32674e84a_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-68c46eb1afb556cc00704af32674e84a_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-18e29df12c2e7dd1c6a568a822551240_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3cb2561df0ff8b18c31a7bfbf34a86c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-18e29df12c2e7dd1c6a568a822551240_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e3cb2561df0ff8b18c31a7bfbf34a86c_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-18e29df12c2e7dd1c6a568a822551240_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-18e29df12c2e7dd1c6a568a822551240_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e营销不是推销 证明不是伪证\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e今年下半年 中普合拍的高中生与哥德巴赫猜想将正式开机 我将继续担任哥德巴赫这一角色 文体两开花\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e==✊=  =✊==\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e————————分割线—————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1.1中午再更\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我现在要发表一些主观的看法了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实，我挺同情他的。有些人说他是中二，对此我不太赞同。从他的描述中，我看到了很强的功利心，他的目的是特招，而不是证明自己比别人强。从他的角度来说，作为一个普通中学（待考证）的普通班的普通学生，升学没有什么捷径可走，只能到知乎上引起一下“轰动”。不像某些人，对数论感兴趣就可以找一个教授辅导，他连论文指导老师都没有。正是资源的不足，使他眼光短浅。我不禁联想到了几个月前集中爆发的论文造假事件，那些人，自己不动脑子，就可以进入优秀学府，而他还要费劲心思地包装自己。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有些人对论文造假得来的特招视而不见，然而，现在看到居然有一个没有指导的民科期望特招，多可笑。于是乎，群聚而笑之。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他的确可笑，但也可悲，那些特招的名额，都被造假论文的“好学生”占了，他没有路，前途是灰暗的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我保存他的证明，不是为了给“愤青”们嘲笑的，而是要让人们记住，是我们现行的特招政策使他变得扭曲，是社会造就了他，和千千万万和他一样的高中生。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e闹剧已终结\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d15d3b40e80837bcdd77362ce4815d59_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"512\" data-rawheight=\"512\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2a4db7b053d3ff86f0733e984d4afde8_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"512\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d15d3b40e80837bcdd77362ce4815d59_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='512'%20height='512'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"512\" data-rawheight=\"512\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2a4db7b053d3ff86f0733e984d4afde8_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"512\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d15d3b40e80837bcdd77362ce4815d59_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-d15d3b40e80837bcdd77362ce4815d59_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a4dc1a1dc5093edb8a25636efd50eead_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6174f601cd5a966c57f3d6ccdc973596_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a4dc1a1dc5093edb8a25636efd50eead_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1125'%20height='2436'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"2436\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6174f601cd5a966c57f3d6ccdc973596_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a4dc1a1dc5093edb8a25636efd50eead_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a4dc1a1dc5093edb8a25636efd50eead_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559649353,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"371a619d850bce68c575cc96e36b4872","url_token":"3de-21ci-fang-82","name":"3的21次方","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-eea6899900108f6df8997685a4fc2051_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-eea6899900108f6df8997685a4fc2051_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/371a619d850bce68c575cc96e36b4872","user_type":"people","headline":"一个碌碌无为的学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559649353","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545747978,"updated_time":1545747978,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":13,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不邀而来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我看过一个笑话，内容差不多就是这样\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想在北京开出租车，但是只有本地人可以开。所以为了在北京开出租车，我努力打拼，起早贪黑，努力工作，找到了一份月收入上万的工作并拿到了北京户口。最后，我辞掉工作，终于满足了我开出租车的心愿。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先，我祝愿你成功。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其次，你太低估哥猜了，而且论文也不是你想象的那么好写的。论文不是作文，哥猜不是瞎猜。不要一个好好的学生成了民科。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，我也保佑你不要下半年开机，文体两开花。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以上\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560246532,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e9b50ab761c9c77e820b054aee2f2ea8","url_token":"xiao-he-e-18","name":"小何哦","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3b30b7f38163e2a378af2befe981200b_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-3b30b7f38163e2a378af2befe981200b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e9b50ab761c9c77e820b054aee2f2ea8","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560246532","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-494ce0c393f801db7042f6325c3a88b8_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545822259,"updated_time":1546320724,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":51,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我们就像他的头像\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c5a554d53c7bc235fd67e1fe36f8573c_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"512\" data-rawheight=\"512\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-35e2284e4d1658e56712532ac36b36e8_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"512\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c5a554d53c7bc235fd67e1fe36f8573c_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='512'%20height='512'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"512\" data-rawheight=\"512\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-35e2284e4d1658e56712532ac36b36e8_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"512\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c5a554d53c7bc235fd67e1fe36f8573c_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-c5a554d53c7bc235fd67e1fe36f8573c_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e大家取关啊啊啊啊！！！！！！！！！！！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为何会有一群沙雕赞他的，快快删掉你们的评论！还前排，还吃瓜，还鼓励他？这群沙雕怕是疯了？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就他那水平上过高中？证nmb呢证？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一月一号如果他的证明错误（那是肯定的），大家记得取关并举报，到时肯定有一堆懒人不取关的，别让数学成为某些人涨粉的手段（ 他这号可值钱了，我看着不爽）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e————————————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e原答案：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e呵呵，还有一堆人支持他我也是醉了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可能那些人对哥德巴赫猜想的难度没什么直观印象。我换一个说法吧，如果题主说自己推翻了相对论，你会怎么想？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然不能一棍子把人全部打倒。但是，但是，令我无法忍受的是他的目的性与他的无知，你们翻他的动态，一个连高中命题高中数列都没搞懂的人能干出什么事情？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e成功的话我吃屎，十车，东风大卡。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e小声逼逼一句：看到题主这睿智，我仿佛看到了当年那个高考零分考生。就是那个不用圆周率算圆的面积还发一堆所谓的论文给大学妄想被保送的那位。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559746632,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"86ad296cdcd57bc655e01e3d9a039b3e","url_token":"lin-yan-zuo","name":"佑佑","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-42303313609b8329bd5a3bbd10b66dff_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-42303313609b8329bd5a3bbd10b66dff_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/86ad296cdcd57bc655e01e3d9a039b3e","user_type":"people","headline":"求学","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559746632","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545758615,"updated_time":1545818216,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":26,"content":"\u003cp\u003e看了评论区和别人的答案，发现大家对于这件事情还是非常包容的。但可能是因为我是学数学的，体会过其中艰辛，目前也正在煎熬。对于什么都没学的中二少年我是略有愤怒，怒其无知又自负。也有对于“这种问题居然还放上来讨论”的不爽，也有对于民科泛滥的怨气。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e希望大家多读点书。引用杨绛先生的一句话：你的问题在于读书不多而想得太多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e------------------------------分割线---------------------------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这种钓鱼贴就应该让他沉下去。这种问题简直就是对学数学的人的侮辱，居然还要1.1号在知乎公开论文。哪里冒出来的民科，真的够了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e给你一句名言：too young too simple sometimes naive\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559820267,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"22013139469948a48a6983a22b362c3c","url_token":"bj365","name":"空一格","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-16bff4cd9b634f213e42a85d121b3c86_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-16bff4cd9b634f213e42a85d121b3c86_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/22013139469948a48a6983a22b362c3c","user_type":"people","headline":"科技创造财富，知识点亮人生。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559820267","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545785674,"updated_time":1545785674,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":33,"content":"\u003cp\u003e酿希匹，别说保送清华北大上研了，当教授都没问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别说在清北当教授了，哈佛数学系都要过来挖你！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e诺贝尔奖里没有数学奖，但是数学有\u003cb\u003e费尔兹奖\u003c/b\u003e啊！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e前些年有个俄罗斯怪才证明了庞加莱猜想，被授予了费尔兹奖。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你要是证明了哥德巴赫猜想，给你授三次费尔兹奖也不为过啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你即使得了一次费尔兹奖，你这倍子直接拿下了，还保什么送啊？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560396125,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c5afca4748da16306298ab39f53fe830","url_token":"da-li-ya-wo-bo-yi","name":"达莉娅沃波依","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-549ed9bfe1448bc096e8d4993312bda3_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-549ed9bfe1448bc096e8d4993312bda3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c5afca4748da16306298ab39f53fe830","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560396125","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545834496,"updated_time":1545834496,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":18,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不要害怕别人说什么，有梦就去追\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很大程度上众人都是抱着看笑话的心态来的，我也一样，但很不幸的是数学这门学科从初等到高等，发展的历史上充斥着偶然性，我怕你真的才华横溢别的不怎么行，偏偏把哥猜给试出来了，这就搞得我们很尴尬，岂不是打脸了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以呢，大家都在看着，你1月1号证出个啥，如果证成了，那别说清北了，哈佛mit绝大多数数学教授在你面前就是个弟弟。可你要证失败了，那就是成民科了，劝你老早回去继续复习，清北真的只是由高考分数决定的，而证实这种东西需要的天才和努力是任何大学都没法比的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可你要是在营销涨粉，我十几个知乎号到时候追着喷的你 都不认识\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563026515,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ff12638c690521491e93d12919f66cb2","url_token":"jetfire","name":"JetfiRex","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/640cda949503ce3d15af32daadc07e4c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/640cda949503ce3d15af32daadc07e4c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ff12638c690521491e93d12919f66cb2","user_type":"people","headline":"IMO30分银牌中国队垫底，变形金刚及歼20脑残粉，DL玩家","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563026515","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546174231,"updated_time":1546174231,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"content":"题主成功创造了2019年第一个热点。\u003cbr\u003e可喜可贺可喜可贺。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560956691,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560956691","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545902024,"updated_time":1545902024,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":24,"content":"\u003cp\u003e小朋友，保送北大清华比证明哥德巴赫猜想容易了N个数量级。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是保送北大的，十多年前了，那会只要你是数学OR物理竞赛集训队的，保送的时候跟招生老师说选北大数学系是没什么压力的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e竞赛想进集训队然后保送清北需要做到什么，两年学完高中所有课程+学完大学专业课+刷茫茫多的竞赛题+一个还算聪明的脑子。想学完这些，基本都是没什么休息时间的，寒暑假周末大半时间都要留校，每天六点起床到11点半睡觉也基本都是看书学习的。虽然艰难，但只要你不笨，而且特别能吃苦爱学习对数理充满兴趣，都还是有希望的。但我从来没觉得自己有生之年能触及那些能在历史长河中留下名字的人的地步，认真体会过就能发现天赋之间的差距几乎是一眼望去看不到顶的绝望。你需要比能保送清北的人平均水平远远超出许多的绝顶天赋+数十年如一日艰苦做科研的心性，也仅仅是有一点希望和可能去获得上帝给与的那一点灵光一闪，解决一些现在这些未曾解决的世界难题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e上清北，你所面对的不过是从全国数百万应届考生中选出几百个这种万分之一的几率而已。这个概率是不大，但对于一般人都是有希望的。但想想证明哥德巴赫猜想那你要竞争的是人类历史上三百多年来所有天赋卓绝的人，说实在的，除非你发现你从小到大都表现的跟超级天才一样，从来没有一个能难得住你的数学问题，不然这个几率就是0.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563778962,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fd14b02e36b45f851664bde239bb01e4","url_token":"zhong-gu-liu-chi","name":"钟鼓琉离","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a989ea81305f46482722519df35a298e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a989ea81305f46482722519df35a298e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fd14b02e36b45f851664bde239bb01e4","user_type":"people","headline":"商法苟，历史，美术，文学，acg","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563778962","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546275905,"updated_time":1546276073,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"\u003cp\u003e恭喜知乎在微博化的大路上又提速了一个档～\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e保北大数学系是没戏了，但是新闻学未尝不可以试试，毕竟客观结果上看，是很成功的营销呢(笑)\u